<body>
<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">
<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>Death Certificate</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen will capture patient death details and it will issue death certificate.
<br /><hr /><br />
<img src="images/mis_deathcertificate.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />

<p>
<span class="title">Service No:  </span><br />
User can write patient service number, it can't remain blank. 
<br />
<span class="title">HIN: </span> <br />
Based on service number user can select HIN Number, it can't remain blank. 
<br />
<span class="title">Ad No: </span> 
<br />Based on service number and HIN Number user can select Admission and discharge number, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Patient Name: </span> 
    <br />Based on service number, HIN Number and admission number patient name will display, user can modify patient name and it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Gender: </span> 
    <br />Based on service number, HIN Number and admission number patient gender will display, user can modify patient gender and it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Date of Death: </span> 
    <br />User can write patient date of death details, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Time of Death: </span> 
    <br />User can write patient time of death details, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Mother’s name: </span> 
    <br />User can write patient mother name details, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Father’s name: </span> 
    <br />User can write patient father name details, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Address of the deceased at the time of death: </span> 
    <br />User can write deceased at the time of death details, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Permanent address of deceased: </span> 
    <br />User can write permanent address of deceased details, it can't remain blank.
    
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Date of registration: </span> 
    <br />User can write certificate date of registration details, it can't remain blank.
     <br />
    <span class="title">Date of issuing: </span> 
    <br />User can write certificate issue date details, it can't remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Registration No: </span> 
    <br />User can write death certificate registration number details, it should be unique number, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Number of copies: </span> 
    <br />User can write number death certificate required for patient, it can't remain blank.

    <br />
    <span class="title">Amount: </span> 
    <br />User can write amount details, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Remarks: </span> 
    <br />User can write remarks or observation details, it can remain blank.

    <br />
    <span class="title">Authenticated Employee: </span> 
    <br />User can select the doctors from the given list, this will come from employee screen, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Submit (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on Submit button user can save the data.


    
</p>



</div>
